177
00:10:31,030 --> 00:10:33,830
Aku akan masuk ke kamarku dan beristirahat sebentar.

178
00:10:33,830 --> 00:10:37,830
Tolong beritahu aku setelah kau mendapatkan hasilnya.

179
00:10:39,330 --> 00:10:41,130
Ya.

180
00:10:48,530 --> 00:10:50,430
